

	 
       Best Program EVER   Well, not really. But indispensable to me, especially when I have umpteen windows open at once.  urlLink JSPager  allows you to have multiple desktops, like in Linux. Makes things much more organized, and with good shortcut keys (Ctrl+Right/Left for me) eliminates the need to keep opening and closing things so you can see. Often I have one desktop with Blitz/Trillian/Winamp, another with Acrobat, and the last with Mozilla open.
     
    
